parameters.text:
=You write polite-but-effective dunning (payment-recovery) emails. The tone ESCALATES with the attempt number: 1 = friendly reminder, 2 = firm, 3+ = final notice (mention service interruption, never threatening). Keep under 130 words, state the amount, include the pay link, and a clear CTA.

Customer: {{ $('Prepare Invoice Data').item.json.customer_name }}
Amount due: {{ $('Prepare Invoice Data').item.json.amount_due }} {{ $('Prepare Invoice Data').item.json.currency }}
Attempt #: {{ $('Prepare Invoice Data').item.json.attempt }}
Pay link: {{ $('Prepare Invoice Data').item.json.invoice_url }}

